trans-unit.source: Indicates whether a control designer requires a preview instance of the control at design time.
trans-unit.target: Angir om kontrollen designer krever en forhåndsvisning av forekomst av kontrollen under utformingen.

trans-unit.source: This class cannot be inherited.
trans-unit.target: Denne klassen kan ikke arves.

trans-unit.source: Apply the SupportsPreviewControlAttribute attribute to a control designer class to indicate the type of preview control that is supported by the control designer.
trans-unit.target: Bruk SupportsPreviewControlAttribute-attributtet til en kontroll designer klasse til å angi kontrolltypen forhåndsvisning som støttes av kontrollen designer.

trans-unit.source: Use this attribute to change a preview control for design-time rendering without affecting the actual persisted instance of the associated control.
trans-unit.target: Bruk dette attributtet til å endre en preview-kontroll for utforming gjengivelse uten å påvirke faktiske faste forekomsten av den tilknyttede kontrollen.

trans-unit.source: Typically, you specify the SupportsPreviewControlAttribute when declaring a custom designer class that is derived from the <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ControlDesigner> class.
trans-unit.target: Vanligvis angir du SupportsPreviewControlAttribute når deklarerer en egendefinert designer klasse som er avledet fra <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ControlDesigner>klassen.</xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ControlDesigner>

trans-unit.source: The value of the <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.SupportsPreviewControlAttribute.SupportsPreviewControl%2A> property for the SupportsPreviewControlAttribute attribute determines the behavior for the <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ControlDesigner.UsePreviewControl%2A> and <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ControlDesigner.ViewControl%2A> members in the base <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ControlDesigner> class.
trans-unit.target: Verdien for <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.SupportsPreviewControlAttribute.SupportsPreviewControl%2A>egenskapen for attributtet SupportsPreviewControlAttribute bestemmer virkemåten for <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ControlDesigner.UsePreviewControl%2A>og <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ControlDesigner.ViewControl%2A>medlemmer i basistabellen <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ControlDesigner>klasse.</xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ControlDesigner> </xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ControlDesigner.ViewControl%2A> </xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ControlDesigner.UsePreviewControl%2A> </xref:System.Web.UI.Design.SupportsPreviewControlAttribute.SupportsPreviewControl%2A>

trans-unit.source: Set the <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.SupportsPreviewControlAttribute.SupportsPreviewControl%2A> property to `true` to indicate that the designer uses a temporary copy of the associated control to generate the design-time HTML.
trans-unit.target: Angi den <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.SupportsPreviewControlAttribute.SupportsPreviewControl%2A>egenskapen `true` til å angi at designer bruker en midlertidig kopi av den tilknyttede kontrollen til å generere HTML utformingen.</xref:System.Web.UI.Design.SupportsPreviewControlAttribute.SupportsPreviewControl%2A>

trans-unit.source: Changes to the temporary control are not persisted.
trans-unit.target: Endre midlertidig kontrollen er ikke opprettholdt.

trans-unit.source: Set the <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.SupportsPreviewControlAttribute.SupportsPreviewControl%2A> property to `false` to indicate that the designer returns the control instance, specifically the <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.ComponentDesigner.Component%2A> property, from the <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ControlDesigner.ViewControl%2A> method.
trans-unit.target: Angi den <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.SupportsPreviewControlAttribute.SupportsPreviewControl%2A>egenskapen `false` til å angi at designer returnerer kontroll-forekomsten, spesielt den <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.ComponentDesigner.Component%2A>egenskapen fra den <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ControlDesigner.ViewControl%2A>metoden.</xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ControlDesigner.ViewControl%2A> </xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.ComponentDesigner.Component%2A> </xref:System.Web.UI.Design.SupportsPreviewControlAttribute.SupportsPreviewControl%2A>

trans-unit.source: Changes to the control object are persisted.
trans-unit.target: Endringer i kontrollobjektet er faste.

trans-unit.source: For example, the <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.CalendarDesigner> class is marked with the SupportsPreviewControlAttribute set to `true`.
trans-unit.target: For eksempel den <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.CalendarDesigner>klasse er merket med SupportsPreviewControlAttribute satt til `true`.</xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.CalendarDesigner>

trans-unit.source: The designer uses the preview control with the automatic style formatting task, which allows the user to preview various autoformat stylesthat can be applied to the calendar.
trans-unit.target: Designer bruker preview-kontroll med stilen automatisk formatering aktiviteten, som gir brukeren mulighet til å forhåndsvise forskjellige fortløpende stylesthat kan brukes i kalenderen.

trans-unit.source: As the user selects different autoformat styles in the user interface, the selected style scheme is applied to the preview control.
trans-unit.target: Brukeren velger annen fortløpende stiler i brukergrensesnittet, brukes valgte stilen skjemaet som preview-kontrollen.

trans-unit.source: Applying a new style to the preview control does not change the scheme that is applied to the instance of the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Calendar> control in the designer.
trans-unit.target: Bruk en ny stil for forhåndsvisning kontrollen ikke endre skjemaet som brukes på forekomsten av den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Calendar>kontrollen i designer.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Calendar>

trans-unit.source: If the SupportsPreviewControlAttribute is not specified in the control designer declaration, the <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ControlDesigner> behavior is equivalent to specifying the <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.SupportsPreviewControlAttribute.SupportsPreviewControl%2A> as `false`.
trans-unit.target: Hvis SupportsPreviewControlAttribute ikke er angitt i kontrollen designer-deklarasjon av <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ControlDesigner>Virkemåte tilsvarer angivelse av <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.SupportsPreviewControlAttribute.SupportsPreviewControl%2A>som `false`.</xref:System.Web.UI.Design.SupportsPreviewControlAttribute.SupportsPreviewControl%2A> </xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ControlDesigner>

trans-unit.source: > [!NOTE] > Designer classes derived from the <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ControlDesigner> class can override the <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ControlDesigner.UsePreviewControl%2A> and <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ControlDesigner.ViewControl%2A> members, and ignore the SupportsPreviewControlAttribute attribute.
trans-unit.target: > [!NOTE] > Designer klasser som er avledet fra den <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ControlDesigner>klassen kan overstyre den <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ControlDesigner.UsePreviewControl%2A>og <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ControlDesigner.ViewControl%2A>medlemmer, og Ignorer attributtet SupportsPreviewControlAttribute.</xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ControlDesigner.ViewControl%2A> </xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ControlDesigner.UsePreviewControl%2A> </xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ControlDesigner>

trans-unit.source: To determine the expected behavior for <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ControlDesigner.ViewControl%2A> and <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ControlDesigner.UsePreviewControl%2A>, see the reference documentation for the derived control designer class.
trans-unit.target: Til å bestemme den forventede virkemåten for <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ControlDesigner.ViewControl%2A>og <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ControlDesigner.UsePreviewControl%2A>Se referansedokumentasjonen for det avledede kontrollen designer-klasse.</xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ControlDesigner.UsePreviewControl%2A> </xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ControlDesigner.ViewControl%2A>

trans-unit.source: For general information about using attributes, see [Attributes Overview](http://msdn.microsoft.com/en-us/a4daf212-2410-423d-a800-7a08864e9bff) and [Attributes](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md).
trans-unit.target: Hvis du vil ha generell informasjon om hvordan du bruker attributter, se [oversikt over attributter](http://msdn.microsoft.com/en-us/a4daf212-2410-423d-a800-7a08864e9bff) og [attributter](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md).

trans-unit.target: Du finner mer informasjon om utformingen attributter [attributter og utformingen støtte](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md).

trans-unit.source: Gets a value indicating whether the control designer requires a temporary preview control at design time.
trans-unit.target: Henter en verdi som angir om kontrollen designer krever en midlertidig preview-kontroll ved utformingen.

trans-unit.source: Typically, you specify a value for the SupportsPreviewControl property by applying the <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.SupportsPreviewControlAttribute> attribute to a custom designer class declaration.
trans-unit.target: Vanligvis, angi en verdi for egenskapen SupportsPreviewControl ved å bruke den <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.SupportsPreviewControlAttribute>attributt til en egendefinert designer klasse-deklarasjon.</xref:System.Web.UI.Design.SupportsPreviewControlAttribute>

trans-unit.source: The value of the SupportsPreviewControl property for the <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.SupportsPreviewControlAttribute> attribute determines the behavior for the <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ControlDesigner.UsePreviewControl%2A> and <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ControlDesigner.ViewControl%2A> members in the base <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ControlDesigner> class.
trans-unit.target: Verdien for egenskapen SupportsPreviewControl for <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.SupportsPreviewControlAttribute>attributtet bestemmer virkemåten for <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ControlDesigner.UsePreviewControl%2A>og <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ControlDesigner.ViewControl%2A>medlemmer i basistabellen <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ControlDesigner>klasse.</xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ControlDesigner> </xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ControlDesigner.ViewControl%2A> </xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ControlDesigner.UsePreviewControl%2A> </xref:System.Web.UI.Design.SupportsPreviewControlAttribute>

trans-unit.source: Set the SupportsPreviewControl property to `true` to indicate that the designer uses a temporary copy of the associated control to generate the design-time HTML.
trans-unit.target: Egenskapen SupportsPreviewControl til `true` til å angi at designer bruker en midlertidig kopi av den tilknyttede kontrollen til å generere HTML utformingen.

trans-unit.source: Changes to the temporary control are not persisted.
trans-unit.target: Endre midlertidig kontrollen er ikke opprettholdt.

trans-unit.source: Set the SupportsPreviewControl property to `false` to indicate that the designer returns the control instance, specifically the <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.ComponentDesigner.Component%2A> property, from the <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ControlDesigner.ViewControl%2A> method.
trans-unit.target: Angi egenskapen SupportsPreviewControl `false` til å angi at designer returnerer kontroll-forekomsten, spesielt den <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.ComponentDesigner.Component%2A>egenskapen fra den <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ControlDesigner.ViewControl%2A>metoden.</xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ControlDesigner.ViewControl%2A> </xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.ComponentDesigner.Component%2A>

trans-unit.target: Endringer i kontrollobjektet er faste.
